{"title":"Ron’s Bikes R-Werks EVOO 29er Pre-Order","link":"https://theradavist.com/rons-bikes-r-werks-evoo-29er-pre-order/","date":1729780123000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-1.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-1.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-1.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-1.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-1.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em>Featured in our </em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-made-bike-show-part-03/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>2024 MADE Bike Show Coverage</em></a><em> and hucked to flat multiple times by John during the documentation, the R-Werks EVOO 29er ($2200) is one tough, rigid mountain bike inspired by the great rim brake bikes of the 1990s and early aughts…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-43.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-43.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-43.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-43.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-43.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1334\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-25.jpg?fit=1200,1334&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-25.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-25.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-25.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/10/2024-MADE-BIke-Show-Rons-Bikes-Alumalith-Evo-25.jpg?resize=1536,1025&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Ron’s Bikes <a href=\"https://ronsbikes.com/products/coming-soon-r-werks-evoo-29er-pre-order\" target=\"_blank\">opened up the pre-order yesterday</a> for these made in Vermont by Frank the Welder frames, kindly requesting half up front now, with delivery in February or March. This includes a frame (sizes small through XL – size large pictured above) and Taper Traxxx steel fork. These bikes feature a modern geometry, inspired by World Cup XC bikes without anything “extra”.</p>\n<p>Check out a wonderful back story on the <a href=\"https://ronsbikesblog.com/2024/10/23/r-werks-evoo-pre-order/\" target=\"_blank\">Ron’s Bikes Blog</a>!</p>\n<p>See all of our detailed photos at our <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2024-made-bike-show-part-03/\" target=\"_blank\">2024 MADE Bike Show Coverage</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/rons-bikes-r-werks-evoo-29er-pre-order/\">Ron’s Bikes R-Werks EVOO 29er Pre-Order</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"09bd1a07b7392c5accdb2c7784b2b14b81032ae92d93056f4140a027720a551d","category":"Cycling"}